OL,3,CMetro disruption due to Gateshead
OL,4,Cflyover closure to continue into New
OL,5,CYear
OL,7,FTyne and Wear Metro operator Nexus has
OL,8,Ftoday (23 December) confirmed that the
OL,9,Fdisruption to its train services
OL,10,Fcaused by the closure of the Gateshead
OL,11,Fflyover will continue until at least
OL,12,Fthe New Year.
OL,14,FTrains between Monument and Heworth
OL,15,Fare currently suspended until further
OL,16,Fnotice, after advice from structural
OL,17,Fengineers. This is because they run
OL,18,Fthrough tunnels underneath the
OL,19,FGateshead flyover.
