OL,7,FNexus has described this as an
OL,8,F"unprecedented situation" and one of
OL,9,Fthe "biggest operational challenges"
OL,10,Fin the history of the Tyne and Wear
OL,11,FMetro.
OL,13,FThe operator has also warned that
OL,14,Fbecause it is unable to maintain the
OL,15,Ftrains that are currently stranded on
OL,16,Fthe south side of the Tyne, it cannot
OL,17,Fguarantee services on that side of the
OL,18,Friver will be able to continue for the
OL,19,Fwhole period the tunnels are closed,
OL,20,Fsaying it needs to be "realistic".
