OL,7,FMeanwhile, the North East Mayor Kim
OL,8,FMcGuinness held an urgent meeting with
OL,9,Fthe Transport Secretary today (23
OL,10,FDecember), to discuss both short-term
OL,11,Fand long-term solutions to the
OL,12,FGateshead flyover situation.
