OL,7,FThe Mayor's office told ITV Tyne Tees:
OL,8,F"The Mayor was meeting the Transport
OL,9,FSecretary tonight in a bid to agree a
OL,10,Fpermanent solution for the flyover.
OL,11,FShe is pushing Gateshead Council to
OL,12,Fbring forward emergency repairs so
OL,13,Fthat Metro trains can start running
OL,14,Fagain through the tunnel under the
OL,15,Fflyover before the new year."
OL,17,FCathy Massarella, managing director of
OL,18,FNexus, said: "The Metro line closure
OL,19,Fremains an evolving situation. We ask
OL,20,Fcustomers to plan in advance and allow
OL,21,Fmore time for their journeys.
