OL,7,F"We're aware of the significant
OL,8,Fdisruption it's causing, however, the
OL,9,Fsafety of our customers and employees
OL,10,Fis our top priority.
OL,12,F"We're sorry for the inconvenience
OL,13,Fcaused. Please be assured we are doing
OL,14,Fall that we can on this, working
OL,15,Fclosely with partners. We will
OL,16,Fcontinue to keep customers updated and
OL,17,Fall the latest information can be
OL,18,Ffound on the Nexus website, the Pop
OL,19,FApp, and on the Metro's X page
OL,20,F(formerly Twitter) @My Metro."
