OL,7,FTyne and Wear Metro services over the
OL,8,Fnext few days have now been confirmed
OL,9,Fby Nexus.
OL,11,FOn Christmas Eve there will be a 15
OL,12,Fminute service frequency north of the
OL,13,FTyne and a 24 minute frequency south
OL,14,Fof the Tyne. Services will start to
OL,15,Frun down from 6pm. There will be an
OL,16,Fhourly service from around 7pm until
OL,17,Fthe end of service.
OL,19,FThere are no Metro services running on
OL,20,FChristmas Day.
