OL,7,FOn Boxing Day there will be a 15
OL,8,Fminute frequency north of the Tyne,
OL,9,Fand a 30 minute frequency south of the
OL,10,FTyne, 8am to 8pm. Extra replacement
OL,11,Fbus services (Number 900) will be
OL,12,Frunning between Monument and Heworth.
OL,14,FFans heading to the Newcastle United
OL,15,Fgame should allow plenty of extra time
OL,16,Fto get to the match. Metro tickets are
OL,17,Falso being accepted on local bus
OL,18,Froutes.
