OL,7,FOver the weekend, Gateshead town
OL,8,Fcentre was reportedly quieter than
OL,9,Fusual, with Metros halted and traffic
OL,10,Fdiverted.
OL,12,FAntonio Pili, owner of Italian
OL,13,Frestaurant Sapori told ITV Tyne Tees:
OL,14,F"Every sort of business relies on the
OL,15,Fweeks coming up to Christmas to be the
OL,16,Fbusiest time of the year as it gets
OL,17,Fquieter in January.
